---
title: Indonesian Style Coconut Diced Chicken Breast Curry with Courgette and Zesty Rice
description: This Indonesian Style Coconut Diced Chicken Breast Curry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220824_R01_W40_UK_R3938-14_KB_Main_swap_low-dff724ac.jpg
